===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*krey-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|cryme}}, {{m|enm|crime}}, from {{der|en|fro|crime}}, {{m|fro|crimne}}, from {{der|en|la|crīmen}}. Displaced native {{cog|ang|firen}}.

